rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Permanent Link: BIRDSTRIKE\">BIRDSTRIKE</a></h3>\n\n<div class=\"entry\">\n<p>I put birdstrike in all caps or all lower case cause I often forget if its one word or two. Anywho, I got yelled at so here&#8217;s a birdstrike update. YAY BIRDSTRIKE!! We had a good show. And if you missed it, then it was a FANTASTIC show, and I hate you forever for missing [...]</p>\n</div>\n\n<p class=\"meta\">Tuesday 28th February 2006 - 3:01:51 AM | <a href=\"http://kelcium.com/2006/02/birdstrike/#comments\" title=\"Comment on BIRDSTRIKE\">Comment (1)</a></p>\n\n</li>\n\n\n\n\n<li><h3><a href=\"http://kelcium.com/2006/02/yay-for-rockapella/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Permanent Link: Yay for Rockapella\">Yay for Rockapella</a></h3>\n\n<div class=\"entry\">\n<p>Uh, if anyone of you wanna sing along&#8230; you all know the words&#8230;.. don&#8217;t. Seriously, it&#8217;s really annoying.</p>\n</div>\n\n<p class=\"meta\">Tuesday 28th February 2006 - 1:56:43 AM | <a href=\"http://kelcium.com/2006/02/yay-for-rockapella/#respond\" title=\"Comment on Yay for Rockapella\">Comment</a></p>\n\n</li>\n\n\n\n\n<li><h3><a href=\"http://kelcium.com/2006/02/its-muh-burfday-no-mo/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Permanent Link: It&#8217;s muh burfday no mo&#8217;\">It&#8217;s muh burfday no mo&#8217;</a></h3>\n\n<div class=\"entry\">\n<p>Yay for a fantastic burfday. I way felt the love. And thanks to the internet I got ridiculous amounts of &#8220;happy birthday!&#8221;s. Thank you myspace and youre birthday icons. Anywayz, as a quick recap here and kinda as a thanks, some pics. Enjoy. Bday celebration numero uno con mis roommates. B-day celebration numero dos con [...]</p>\n</div>\n\n<p class=\"meta\">Wednesday 22nd February 2006 - 2:18:46 AM | <a href=\"http://kelcium.com/2006/02/its-muh-burfday-no-mo/#comments\" title=\"Comment on It&#8217;s muh burfday no mo&#8217;\">Comment (1)</a></p>\n\n</li>\n\n\n\n\n<li><h3><a href=\"http://kelcium.com/2006/02/its-my-birthday-in-new-york/