ne for that part DM: dang DM: depends, was i hired for that job? DM: cause then i can go!</p>\n</div>\n\n<p class=\"meta\">Friday 10th February 2006 - 12:24:51 AM | <a href=\"http://kelcium.com/2006/02/birthday-planning/#respond\" title=\"Comment on Birthday planning\">Comment</a></p>\n\n</li>\n\n\n\n\n<li><h3><a href=\"http://kelcium.com/2006/02/oh-how-much-i-dont-miss-spanish/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Permanent Link: Oh, how much I don&#8217;t miss spanish\">Oh, how much I don&#8217;t miss spanish</a></h3>\n\n<div class=\"entry\">\n<p>Away message (which never appears when I&#8217;m trying to make a joke): &#8220;Cualquier cosa es m\u00c3\u00a1s significativo cuando est\u00c3\u00a1 escrita en un idioma extranjero.&#8221; -Anything is more significant when written in a foreign language. Me: aye dios mios! Que langua es el away message que nada appearo cuando yo quiero lo. ah, mi espanol no [...]</p>\n</div>\n\n<p class=\"meta\">Wednesday 8th February 2006 - 1:43:34 AM | <a href=\"http://kelcium.com/2006/02/oh-how-much-i-dont-miss-spanish/#respond\" title=\"Comment on Oh, how much I don&#8217;t miss spanish\">Comment</a></p>\n\n</li>\n\n\n\n\n<li><h3><a href=\"http://kelcium.com/2006/02/i-think-i-got-jewed/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Permanent Link: I think I got Jewed\">I think I got Jewed</a></h3>\n\n<div class=\"entry\">\n<p>A softer world is one of the funniest online comics I&#8217;ve seen in a while. Go you a softer world. *warning: some are crazy funny, some are just weird&#8230;just like every comedy thing</p>\n</div>\n\n<p class=\"meta\">Tuesday 7th February 2006 - 1:39:13 AM | <a href=\"http://kelcium.com/2006/02/i-think-i-got-jewed/#respond\" title=\"Comment on I think I got Jewed\">Comment</a></p>\n\n</li>\n\n\n\n\n<li><h3><a href=\"http://kelcium.com/2006/02/its-prince-yall/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Permanent Link: It&#8217;s Prince ya&#8217;ll~~~~\">It&#8217;s Prince ya&#8217;ll~~~~</a></h3>\n\n<div class=\"entry\">\n<p>Maya had HUGE boobs!!! Steve Martin was gold.</p>\n</div>\n\n<p class=\"meta\">Sunday 5th February 2006 - 5:10:58 PM | <a href=\"http://kelcium.com/2006/02/its-prince-yall/#respond\" title=\"Comment on It&#8217;s Prince ya&#8217;ll~~~~\">Comment</a></p>\n\n</li>\n\n\n\n\n<li><h3><a href=\"http://kelcium.com/2006/02/oscar-nominated-best-supporting-nipple/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Permanent Link: Oscar Nominated Best Supporting Nipple\">Oscar Nominated Best Supporting Nipple</a></h3>\n\n<div class=\"entry\">\n<p>Went out partyin&#8217; last night. woo. Prentending to be drunk is oddly tiring. It was like one big imrpov game though. anywho&#8230; This post, not funny. But I will tell you who is funny, Rick Moranis. Surprised? Yeah me too. No idea if his new album is funny, but he made me laugh on Conan.</p>\n</div>\n\n<p class=\"meta\">Saturday 4th February 2006 - 2:22:57 PM | <a href=\"http://kelcium.com/2006/02/oscar-nominated-best-supporting-nipple/#respond\" title=\"Comment on Oscar Nominated Best Supporting Nipple\">Comment</a></p>\n\n</li>\n\n\n\n</ul></div>\n\n\n        \n</div>\n</div>\n\n<!-- begin sidebar -->\n\n\n<div id=\"topmenu\">\n<ul>\n<li><a id=\"current\" href=\"http://kelcium.com\">Home</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#\" >Archives</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#\">Links</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#\">Contact</a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n\n<div id=\"menu\">\n<ul>\n\n<li id=\"search\">Search<form id=\"searchform\" method=\"get\" action=\"/index.php\">\n<div>\n<input type=\"text\" name=\"s\" id=\"s\" size=\"15\" /><input type=\"submit\" value=\"Go\" />\n</div>\n</form>\n</li>\n\n<!-- <li id=\"calendar\">\n<ul>\n<li></li>\n</ul>\n</li> -->\n\n\n<li id=\"pages\">Pages<ul>\n</ul>\n</li>\n\n<li id=\"categories\">Categories<ul>\n    <li class=\"cat-item cat-item-1\"><a href=\"http://kelcium.com/category/uncategorized/\" title=\"View all posts filed under Uncategorized\">Uncategorized</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n\n<li id=\"archives\">Archives<ul>\n    <li><a href=''http://kelcium.com/2007/06/'' title=''J