om/block-captains\" title=\"Block Captains\"><span class=\"l\"></span><span class=\"r\"></span><span class=\"t\">Block Captains</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"page_item page-item-19 current_page_item\"><a class=\"active\" href=\"http://harborviewhomeownersassociation.com/park-news\" title=\"Park News\"><span class=\"l\"></span><span class=\"r\"></span><span class=\"t\">Park News</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"page_item page-item-29\"><a href=\"http://harborviewhomeownersassociation.com/photos\" title=\"Photos\"><span class=\"l\"></span><span class=\"r\"></span><span class=\"t\">Photos</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"page_item page-item-36\"><a href=\"http://harborviewhomeownersassociation.com/activities\" title=\"Activities\"><span class=\"l\"></span><span class=\"r\"></span><span class=\"t\">Activities</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"page_item page-item-47\"><a href=\"http://harborviewhomeownersassociation.com/contact-us\" title=\"Contact Us\"><span class=\"l\"></span><span class=\"r\"></span><span class=\"t\">Contact Us</span></a></li>\n    </ul>\n</div>\n<div class=\"art-contentLayout\">\n<div class=\"art-content\">\n\n \n<div class=\"art-Post\">\n    <div class=\"art-Post-tl\"></div>\n    <div class=\"art-Post-tr\"></div>\n    <div class=\"art-Post-bl\"></div>\n    <div class=\"art-Post-br\"></div>\n    <div class=\"art-Post-tc\"></div>\n    <div class=\"art-Post-bc\"></div>\n    <div class=\"art-Post-cl\"></div>\n    <div class=\"art-Post-cr\"></div>\n    <div class=\"art-Post-cc\"></div>\n    <div class=\"art-Post-body\">\n<div class=\"art-Post-inner art-article\">\n<h2 class=\"art-PostHeader\">\n  <img src=\"http://harborviewhomeownersassociation.com/wp-content/themes/harborview/images/PostHeaderIcon.png\" width=\"26\" height=\"25\" alt=\"\" />\n<a href=\"http://harborviewhomeownersassociation.com/park-news\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Permanent Link to Park News\">\nPark News</a>\n</h2>\n<div class=\"art-PostContent\">\n\n          <p><strong><font class=\"Apple-style-span\" color=\"#000000\" face=\"arial, helvetica, sans-serif\" size=\"4\"><span class=\"Apple-style-span\" style=\"font-size: 14px\">CHRISTMAS&nbsp; TRIM-A-TREE</span></font></strong></p>\n<p><strong><font class=\"Apple-style-span\" color=\"#000000\" face=\"arial, helvetica, sans-serif\" size=\"4\"><span class=\"Apple-style-span\" style=\"font-size: 14px\">A lively group go together for a trim-a-tree party at the clubhouse.&nbsp; The tree was trimmed and decorations put inside and outside the clubhouse.&nbsp; Everyone said they had a good time and enjoying the snacks was a plus.</span></font></strong></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong><font class=\"Apple-style-span\" color=\"#000000\" face=\"arial, helvetica, sans-serif\" size=\"4\"><span class=\"Apple-style-span\" style=\"font-size: 14px\">CLUBHOUSE&nbsp; BIG SCREEN&nbsp; T V</span></font></strong></p>\n<p><strong><font class=\"Apple-style-span\" color=\"#000000\" face=\"arial, helvetica, sans-serif\" size=\"4\"><span class=\"Apple-style-span\" style=\"font-size: 14px\">If you have not noticed there is a new flat screen&nbsp; T&nbsp; V&nbsp;&nbsp; in the&nbsp; clubhouse.&nbsp; Thank you ELS.&nbsp; The new T V has Blue Ray and HDMI&nbsp; inputs so we should be able to get some interesting games to play on it and it will be great for movies, sports events, and such.</span></font></strong></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong><font class=\"Apple-style-span\" color=\"#000000\" face=\"arial, helvetica, sans-serif\" size=\"4\"><span class=\"Apple-style-span\" style=\"font-size: 14px\">CHRISTMAS TRIMMINGS</span></font></strong></p>\n<p><strong><font class=\"Apple-style-span\" color=\"#000000\" face=\"arial, helvetica, sans-serif\" size=\"4\"><span class=\"Apple-style-span\" style=\"font-size: 14px\">Take a look around the park.&nbsp; A number of the residents have all ready put up lights.&nbsp; Looks great!&nbsp; lets see how many decorated homes we can have this year.&nbsp; Lets make it a big Christmas holiday season.</span></font></strong></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span _fck_bookmark=\"1\" style=\"display: none\"><br />\n    </span></p>\n<p><span _fck_bookmark=\"1\" style=\"display: none\">&nbsp;</span><span _fck_bookmark=\"1\" style=\"display: none\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p><span class=''st_sharethis'' st_title=''Park News'' st_url=''http://harborviewhomeownersassociation.com/park-news'' displayText=''ShareThis''></span></p>                  \n</div>\n<div class=\"cleared\"></div>\n\n</div>\n\n        <div class=\"cleared\"></div>\n    </div>\n</div>\n\n\n<!-- You can start editing here. -->\n\n\n            <!-- If comments are open, but there are no comments. -->\n\n     \n\n<div class=\"art-Post\">\n    <div class=\"art-Post-tl\"></div>\n    <div class=\"art-Post-tr\"></div>\n    <div class=\"art-Post-bl\"></div>\n    <div class=\"art-Post-br\"></div>\n    <div class=\"art-Post-tc\"></div>\n    <div class=\"art-Post-bc\"></div>\n    <div class=\"art-Post-cl\"></div>\n    <div class=\"art-Post-cr\"></div>\n    <div class=\"art-Post-cc\"></div>\n    <div class=\"art-Post-body\">\n<div class=\"art-Post-inner art-article\">\n\n<div class=\"art-PostContent\">\n\n<div id=\"respond\">\n  \n  <h3>Leave a Reply</h3>\n\n<div class=\"cancel-comment-reply\">\n    <small><a rel=\"nofollow\" id=\"cancel-comment-reply-link\" href=\"/park-news#respond\" style=\"display:none;\">Click here to cancel reply.</a></small>\n</div>\n\n\n<form action=\"http://harborviewhomeownersassociation.com/wp-comments-post.php\" method=\"post\" id=\"commentform\">\n\n\n<p><input type=\"text\" name=\"author\" id=\"author\" value=\"\" size=\"22\" tabindex=\"1\" aria-required=''true'' />\n<label for=\"author\"><small>Name (required)</small></label></p>\n\n<p><input type=\"text\" name=\"email\" id=\"email\" value=\"\" size=\"22\" tabindex=\"2\" aria-required=''true'' />\n<label for=\"email\"><small>Mail (will not be published) (required)</small></label></p>\n\n<p><input type=\"text\" na